query:
SELECT p.id, p.nome, p.projectId, p.totalClientes,
       (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM clientes c WHERE c.pesquisaId = p.id) as clientes_reais
FROM pesquisas p
WHERE p.nome = 'Ground'
LIMIT 5
